{"text_id":76193,"tokens":["Two"," handed"," swords"," are"," a"," lot"," of"," fun"," to"," use",","," but"," can"," be"," tricky"," to"," get"," used"," to","."," This"," guide"," will"," tell"," you"," everything"," you"," need"," to"," know"," about"," using"," any"," two"," handed"," sword",".","\n\n","Step"," ","1",":"," Choosing"," a"," Sword","\n","S","words"," come"," in"," many"," different"," shapes"," and"," sizes",","," so"," it","'","s"," important"," to"," choose"," one"," that","'","s"," comfortable"," for"," you"," to"," use","."," If"," you","'","re"," new"," to"," sword"," fighting",","," it","'","s"," best"," to"," start"," with"," a"," smaller"," sword"," so"," you"," can"," get"," used"," to"," the"," feel"," of"," it"," in"," your"," hands","."," Once"," you","'","re"," more"," experienced",","," you"," can"," move"," on"," to"," larger"," swords",".","\n\n","Step"," ","2",":"," Gri","pping"," the"," Sword","\n","Gri","pping"," the"," sword"," is"," key"," to"," using"," it"," effectively","."," You"," want"," to"," hold"," the"," sword"," with"," both"," hands",","," one"," on"," the"," handle"," and"," one"," on"," the"," blade","."," This"," will"," give"," you"," the"," most"," control"," over"," the"," sword",".","\n\n","You"," also"," want"," to"," make"," sure"," that"," you","'","re"," holding"," the"," sword"," evenly"," on"," both"," sides","."," This"," will"," help"," you"," to"," keep"," it"," balanced"," and"," stable",".","\n\n","Step"," ","3",":"," St","ances","\n","There"," are"," a"," few"," different"," stances"," you"," can"," use"," to"," hold"," the"," sword","."," The"," most"," common"," is"," the"," \"","standard","\""," stance",","," where"," you"," stand"," with"," your"," feet"," shoulder"," width"," apart",","," and"," hold"," the"," sword"," in"," front"," of"," you"," with"," both"," hands",".","\n\n","Another"," stance"," is"," the"," \"","ready","\""," stance",","," where"," you"," stand"," with"," your"," feet"," shoulder"," width"," apart",","," and"," hold"," the"," sword"," behind"," you"," with"," both"," hands","."," This"," stance"," is"," used"," to"," prepare"," for"," an"," attack",".","\n\n","The"," last"," stance"," is"," the"," \"","def","ensive","\""," stance",","," where"," you"," stand"," with"," your"," feet"," shoulder"," width"," apart",","," and"," hold"," the"," sword"," in"," front"," of"," you"," with"," one"," hand","."," This"," stance"," is"," used"," to"," block"," an"," attack","."],"sub_source":"wikihow","model":"cohere","label":1}